PrecisORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1997-NO. 4,) which prohibits entry and staking mining claims or prospecting for precious metals on certain lands (approximately 123.8 hectares) near kilometre 281.4 of the Klondike Highway, (Highway No.2) in the Yukon Territory.
